  "description": "<p>尽管还有不少工作要做，但是在酷似昆虫的微型机器人方面，来自哈佛大学微型机器人实验室的最新原型正在大踏步前进。<strong>该实验室最近展示了其最新的HAMR四足机器人，虽然它只有1.7英寸(4.4cm)大小，却能够以8.4倍于体长的秒速奔跑。</strong>通过简单地缩放设计文件，他们甚至能够生产出只有一枚硬币大小的微型机器人(体重仅270mg)。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d947f1f/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241957.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%2B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6HAMR%E6%98%86%E8%99%AB%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241957.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%2B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6HAMR%E6%98%86%E8%99%AB%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241957.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%2B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6HAMR%E6%98%86%E8%99%AB%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241957.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%2B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6HAMR%E6%98%86%E8%99%AB%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F241957.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%2B%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%5D%E5%93%88%E4%BD%9B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6HAMR%E6%98%86%E8%99%AB%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA\" targe